;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;👇🏻&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;①不吃被水淹过或受污染的食品；&lt;br&gt;②不吃因停电解冻过久而腐败的食物；&lt;br&gt;③不使用未经清洗消毒的餐具；&lt;br&gt;④不喝生水，注意饮用水卫生；&lt;br&gt;⑤不吃生食，生熟分开，煮熟煮透；&lt;br&gt;⑥不要采食野蘑菇、野菜；&lt;br&gt;⑦要注重卫生，保持清洁。&lt;a href=&quot;https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&quot; data-hide=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;surl-text&quot;&gt;#小卫唠健康#&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; （广东疾控）&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;暴雨天下班后速速回家，路上注意安全！&lt;span class=&quot;url-icon&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;[开学季]&quot; src=&quot;https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/72/2021_kaixueji_org.png&quot; style=&quot;width:1em; height:1em;&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;img style=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hp0wkjbksoj20sg0sggnn.jpg&quot; referrerpolicy=&quot;no-referrer&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description><link>https://weibo.com/2831150640/Ob4c0wZhH</link><guid isPermaLink="false">https://weibo.com/2831150640/Ob4c0wZhH</guid><pubDate>Tue, 23 Apr 2024 09:39:54 GMT</pubDate><author>深圳卫健委</author></item></channel></rss>